派拉蒙影業和合資者{{le|天空之舞製片公司|Skydance Productions}}在2009年10月與演員[[克里斯·潘恩|克里斯·潘恩]]洽談，邀他在電影中扮演取自[[湯姆·克蘭西|湯姆·克蘭西]]，但不包含於任何小說的角色——[[傑克·萊恩|傑克·萊恩]]。當時，製作人{{le|羅倫佐·狄·邦奈凡杜洛|Lorenzo di Bonaventura}}和{{le|麥斯·紐菲爾|Mace Neufeld}}採用{{le|侯賽因·阿米尼|Hossein Amini}}最初的概念。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Michael|title=Chris Pine in talks for Jack Ryan role|url=http://variety.com/2009/film/news/chris-pine-in-talks-for-jack-ryan-role-1118009912/|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2009-10-13|archivedate=2014-08-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814012225/http://variety.com/2009/film/news/chris-pine-in-talks-for-jack-ryan-role-1118009912/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[傑克·本德|傑克·本德]]在2010年8月是首位根據亞當·柯札德（Adam Cozad）暫名為《莫斯科》的腳本，執導這部片的導演。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title='Lost's Jack Bender Is Jack Ryan Frontrunner|url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/08/losts-jack-bender-jack-ryan-frontrunner/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2010-08-02|archivedate=2013-11-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104094352/http://www.deadline.com/2010/08/losts-jack-bender-jack-ryan-frontrunner/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在隨後的幾個月，作家{{le|安東尼·佩卡姆|Anthony Peckham}}進行改寫，<ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Boris|title=Toronto: Paramount taps 'Sherlock Holmes' scribe for Jack Ryan spy thriller (exclusive)|url=http://heatvision.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/09/tiff-paramount-taps-sherlock-holmes-scribe-for-jack-ryan-spy-thriller-exclusive.html|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2010-09-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922193823/http://heatvision.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/09/tiff-paramount-taps-sherlock-holmes-scribe-for-jack-ryan-spy-thriller-exclusive.html|archivedate=2010-09-22|accessdate=2014-08-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>之後寫《[[迫切的危機_(電影)|迫切的危機]]》[[劇本|劇本]]的{{le|史蒂夫·澤里安|Steve Zaillian}}也加入了改寫的行列。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title=Steve Zaillian On To Rewrite Jack Ryan|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/steve-zaillian-on-to-rewrite-jack-ryan/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2011-02-02|archivedate=2014-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712230543/http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/steve-zaillian-on-to-rewrite-jack-ryan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，澤里安在幾個禮拜後退出，且該片的進度也因潘恩要在《[[闇黑無界：星際爭霸戰|闇黑無界：星際爭霸戰]]》中飾演[[詹姆士·T·寇克|詹姆士·T·寇克]]一角，而被派拉蒙影業擱置了。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title=Script Delays Puts 'Star Trek' Sequel Before Jack Ryan For Chris Pine And Paramount|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/03/script-delays-puts-star-trek-sequel-before-jack-ryan-for-chris-pine-and-paramount/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2011-03-28|archivedate=2014-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712232727/http://www.deadline.com/2011/03/script-delays-puts-star-trek-sequel-before-jack-ryan-for-chris-pine-and-paramount/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此期間，[[大衛·柯普|大衛·柯普]]開始改寫劇本，<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Mike, Jr.|title=Jack Ryan Getting David Koepp Rewrite|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/04/jack-ryan-getting-david-koepp-rewrite/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2013-12-30|date=2011-04-28|archivedate=2013-11-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104203424/http://www.deadline.com/2011/04/jack-ryan-getting-david-koepp-rewrite/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而開拍日期計畫於2012年下半年。<ref>{{cite web|last=Schaefer|first=Sandy|title=Angelina Jolie Not Set For 'Salt 2'; Jack Ryan Reboot Update|url=http://screenrant.com/salt-2-angelina-jolie-jack-ryan-reboot-update-sandy-157745/|publisher=Screen Rant|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2012-03-05|archivedate=2014-04-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425163208/http://screenrant.com/salt-2-angelina-jolie-jack-ryan-reboot-update-sandy-157745/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

導演本德在2012年3月因為行程衝突而退出，造成此片的拍攝再度停擺。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gallagher|first=Brian|title=Untitled Jack Ryan Project Loses Director Jack Bender|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/untitled-jack-ryan-project-loses-director-jack-bender|publisher=MovieWeb|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2012-03-19|archivedate=2013-11-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105122319/http://www.movieweb.com/news/untitled-jack-ryan-project-loses-director-jack-bender|dead-url=no}}</ref>派拉蒙影業為了要在潘恩於2012年9月拍完《闇黑無界：星際爭霸戰》後，立即開始攝製，便很快地聘請了[[肯尼斯·布萊納|肯尼斯·布萊納]]來取代本德。 <ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title=Kenneth Branagh targets Par's Jack Ryan pic|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/kenneth-branagh-targets-par-s-jack-ryan-pic-1118051966/|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2012-03-27|archivedate=2014-03-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330150842/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/kenneth-branagh-targets-par-s-jack-ryan-pic-1118051966/|dead-url=no}}</ref>「我拿到了腳本，它非常引人入勝，而我也知道前幾部作品，我將會讀一些相關書籍，就是如此出乎意料的簡單」布萊納表示。「我原本將要製作另一部電影，但在這一部找上我後便推辭了，且我讀完後有非常強烈的感受，這是那種我會去劇院欣賞的電影。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Fienberg|first=Daniel|title=Set Visit Preview: Kenneth Branagh and Chris Pine are rebooting 'Jack Ryan'|url=http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/set-visit-preview-kenneth-branagh-and-chris-pine-are-rebooting-jack-ryan|publisher=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2013-01-07|archivedate=2013-11-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103232407/http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/set-visit-preview-kenneth-branagh-and-chris-pine-are-rebooting-jack-ryan|dead-url=no}}</ref>

