== 發行 ==
本片最初計畫在2013年12月25日上映，<ref>{{cite web|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|title=Kenneth Branagh's 'Jack Ryan' to Hit Theaters Christmas Day 2013|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kenneth-branaghs-jack-ryan-hit-365627|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=2013-09-02|date=2012-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617215837/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kenneth-branaghs-jack-ryan-hit-365627|archive-date=2013-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>但之後因為派拉蒙影業要在當日發行[[馬丁·史柯西斯|馬丁·史柯西斯]]的《[[華爾街之狼|華爾街之狼]]》，而被推遲至一月。<ref>{{cite web|last=Derschowitz|first=Jessica|title="Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit" moving to January 2014|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57609286/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-moving-to-january-2014/|work=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|publisher=[[CBS|CBS]]|accessdate=2013-10-30|date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029145800/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57609286/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-moving-to-january-2014/|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後被暫定在美國[[馬丁·路德·金紀念日|馬丁·路德·金紀念日]]之前的2014年1月17日發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/official-jack-ryan-moving-january-650181|title=It's Official: Jack Ryan Moving to January 2014|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106052152/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/official-jack-ryan-moving-january-650181|archive-date=2013-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>派拉蒙影業在2013年8月開始以《Jack Ryan: Shadow One》之名推出一部預告片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/new-jack-ryan-film-likely-titled-jack-ryan-shadow-one/|title=New Jack Ryan Film Likely Titled 'Jack Ryan: Shadow One'|date=2013-08-26|accessdate=2013-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826163245/http://www.slashfilm.com/new-jack-ryan-film-likely-titled-jack-ryan-shadow-one/|archive-date=2013-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年10月2日，[[湯姆·克蘭西|湯姆·克蘭西]]逝世後的隔天，首個電影海報以《傑克萊恩︰詭影任務》之名推出。<ref>{{cite web|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|title=Chris Pine Takes a Knee in First Poster for 'Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit'|url=http://collider.com/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-movie-poster/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=2013-10-02|date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005002218/http://collider.com/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-movie-poster|archive-date=2013-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>而首部[[預告片|預告片]]也在是日推出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/video/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-trailer-210023496.html|title='Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit' Theatrical Trailer|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo! Movies]]|date=2013-10-02|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107153741/http://movies.yahoo.com/video/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-trailer-210023496.html|archive-date=2013-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本片之後於2014年5月20日在家用媒體市場推出[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]格式。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit - Amazon Instant Video|url=http://www.amazon.com/Jack-Ryan-Recruit-Chris-Pine/dp/B00HZ3BGPS/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1400647810&sr=8-2&keywords=jack+ryan+shadow+recruit|accessdate=2014-05-21|date=2014-05-20}}</ref>而[[DVD|DVD]]與[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]則是在6月10日由{{le|派拉蒙家庭娛樂公司|Paramount Home Entertainment}}發行。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit Blu-ray|url=http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=13484|publisher=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=2014-03-17|date=2014-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704051649/http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=13484|archive-date=2014-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===評價===
《傑克萊恩：詭影任務》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據158條評論持有55％的新鮮度，平均評分為5.7／10。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jack_ryan_shadow_recruit/|title=Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit (2013)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] ([[Flixster|Flixster]])|accessdate=2014-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140210061220/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jack_ryan_shadow_recruit/|archive-date=2014-02-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於100位評論者，得分57（滿分100），持有36條評論。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit |title=Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119050721/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/jack-ryan-shadow-recruit |archive-date=2014-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在CinemaScore上，觀眾給了電影「B」的評價。

===票房===
《傑克萊恩：詭影任務》在美國和加拿大的首映日上獲得了540萬美元，<ref>{{cite web|last=Mendelson|first=Scott|title=Friday Box Office: 'Ride Along' ($14.5m) Crushes 'Jack Ryan' ($5.4m)|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/01/18/friday-box-office-kevin-hart-is-now-a-movie-star-as-ride-along-earns-14-5m/|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|publisher=Forbes Publishing|accessdate=2014-01-21|date=2014-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121081643/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/01/18/friday-box-office-kevin-hart-is-now-a-movie-star-as-ride-along-earns-14-5m/|archive-date=2014-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於週末結束票房共得1720萬美元。<ref>{{cite web|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|title=Box Office: 'Ride Along' Arrests Top Spot, 'Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit' Stays Undercover|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/box-office-ride-along-arrests-top-spot-jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-stays-undercover-20140119|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|publisher=[[Snagfilms|Snagfilms]]|accessdate=2014-01-21|date=2014-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123005054/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/box-office-ride-along-arrests-top-spot-jack-ryan-shadow-recruit-stays-undercover-20140119|archive-date=2014-01-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在電影的首映周末，有三分之一的觀眾為50歲，25歲以下的觀眾只有15％多，代表儘管是[[克里斯·潘恩|克里斯·潘恩]]所主演的，本電影未能吸引年輕族群觀眾。<ref>{{cite web|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|title='Jack Ryan' Franchise in Question After Snub From Younger Moviegoers|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jack-ryan-franchise-question-snub-672533|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=2014-01-21|date=2014-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122071423/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jack-ryan-franchise-question-snub-672533|archive-date=2014-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BOM2">{{cite web|last=Subers|first=Ray|title=Weekend Report: 'Ride Along' Cruises to January Record|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3774&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo (IMDb)|accessdate=2014-01-21|date=2014-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121012121/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3774&p=.htm|archive-date=2014-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>為2014年第二十四部最高票房的電影，並成為今年第一部已達到了全球票房超過1億美元的電影。<ref>{{cite web|title=2014 Domestic Grosses|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2014&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo (IMDb)|accessdate=2014-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013132815/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2014&p=.htm|archive-date=2019-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>國內票房為5057萬7412美元，海外為8492萬6336美元，全球共計1億3550萬3748美元。<ref>[http://www.boxofficemojo.com/search/?q=Jack%20ryan:%20shadow%20recruit Jack Ryan: Shadow Recruit] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/search/?q=Jack%20ryan:%20shadow%20recruit |date=20140913150107 }}. Box Office Mojo. Retrieved March 3, 2014.</ref>

